\"\" width=\"213\" height=\"300\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-125\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18813527_767512996762763_4180304426396238683_n-209x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"209\" height=\"300\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-126\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18814115_767512493429480_7776109680384457628_n-300x215.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"215\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-127\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18700007_767512480096148_5828022864339596837_n-214x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"214\" height=\"300\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-128\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18767904_767512456762817_7507161074677988502_n-211x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"211\" height=\"300\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-129\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18739656_767512286762834_3674166791206298866_n-300x213.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"213\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-130\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18765823_767512246762838_5520932233753582686_n-211x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"211\" height=\"300\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-131\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18739970_767512230096173_3748537186704123680_n-213x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"213\" height=\"300\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-132\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18813566_767512170096179_1927015942975364727_n-207x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"207\" height=\"300\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-133\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18767527_767511563429573_2372124173377320080_n-209x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"209\" height=\"300\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-134\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18699975_767511553429574_1140650792430399630_n-207x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"207\" height=\"300\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-135\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18740388_767511543429575_2906660182846082648_n-209x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"209\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nမြန်မာနိုင်ငံ၏<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> နံပါတ်တစ်</span> ကျန်းမာရေး ပြဿနာမှာ <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">ထိခိုက်ဒဏ်ရာ</span>ကြောင့် ဖြစ်သည်။\r\nမြန်မာနိုင်ငံတွင် ၂၀၁၆-ခုနှစ်က ယာဉ်တိုက်မှုကြောင့် သေဆုံး(၄၆၀၀)ကျော်၊ ဒဏ်ရာရ(၂၆၀၀၀)ကျော်\r\nတစ်နေ့ လူ(၁၃)ယောက် လမ်းမပေါ် မှာ သေဆုံးနေ ။ အသက် (၁၅-၄၅)နှစ် တွင် အများဆုံး ထိခိုက် ဒဏ်ရာရ။\r\nကမ္ဘာပေါ်တွင် ယာဉ်တိုက်မှုကြောင့် တစ်နှစ်လျင် လူ သေဆုံး ( ၁.၂၅ )-သန်း ကျော်၊ ဒဏ်ရာရသူသန်း (၄၀-၅၀)၊ တစ်နေ့ လူ(၃၀၀၀)ကျော်် လမ်းမပေါ် မှာ သေဆုံးနေ။\r\nယာဉ်တိုက်မှုကြောင့် လူတစ်သိန်းလျင် သေဆုံးနှုန်း ကမ္ဘာပေါ်တွင် (၁၇.၄)ယောက်၊ အရှေ့တောင်အာရှ (၁၇ )ယောက်၊ မြန်မာ(၂၀.၃)ယောက်၊ ထိုင်း (၃၆.၂)ယောက်၊ လစ်ဗျား (၇၃.၄)ယောက်၊\r\n<span style=\"color: #339966;\">credit to Dr Zaw Wai Soe,ပါမောက္ခချုပ်၊ ဆေးတက္ကသိုလ်(၁)၊ ရန်ကုန်။</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-136\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18893476_769332253247504_5954997499699342290_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-137\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18839269_769332276580835_2359966407963272453_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-151\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18835699_769335966580466_4616210605938681984_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-150\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18813942_769337636580299_4742087823773505555_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-149\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18767823_769343943246335_7885416145969009271_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-148\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18767495_769344499912946_7083085379915349020_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-147\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18920535_769347163246013_7407687947352666704_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-146\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18892950_769347199912676_4935059826986407307_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-145\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18835559_769355406578522_6762200039095341221_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-144\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18839036_769355489911847_992666998605668867_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-143\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18813710_769356123245117_795803763898989108_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-142\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18839261_769358583244871_733240531548623834_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-141\" src=\"https://healthformyanmar.tk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/18835789_769360689911327_6239314393144044301_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-140\" src=\"https://hea